Package com.adobe.livecycle.ibmfilenetcontentrepositoryconnector.client.type

The com.adobe.livecycle.ibmfilenetcontentrepositoryconnector.client.type package provides data types and exceptions used when implementing the connector for IBM FileNet Content Repository service.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IGetLinkedLCAssetsLocationResult Stores the output of getLinkedLCAssetsLocation.
ILoginSettings Interface for logon settings, to invoke IBM FileNet Content Repository Connector Service
IPropertyInfo This class stores information for a given property.
IPropertyValueInfo This class stores information about a given property's value and description.
IRetrieveContentResult Stores the output of the retrieveContent and retrieveContentInWorkflow operations.
IStoreContentResult Stores the output of storeContent and storeContentInWorkflow operations.

UpdateVersionType Allows you to increment document version numbers.
